bn-BD.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
bn-BD.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

da-DK.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

de-DE.footer.mission: Origin baut die Sharing Economy von Morgen. Käufer und Verkäufer sind dadurch in der Lage ohne teure Zwischenhändler zu handeln. Wir glauben an die Senkung der Transaktionskosten, freien und transparenten Handeln und frühe Teilnehmer an dem Netzwerk zu beteiligen.

de-DE.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Ihr Produkt oder Dienstleistung verwendet ein Schema, um seine Attribute wie Name, Beschreibung und Preis zu beschreiben. Origin verfügt bereits über mehrere Schemas, die bekannten Kategorien von Auflistungen wie Unterkünfte, Auto und Dienstleistungen zugeordnet sind.

el-GR.footer.mission: Η Origin χτίζει την συνεργατική οικονομία του αύριο. Αγοραστές και πωλητές θα έχουν την δυνατότητα να συναλλάσσονται χωρίς μεσάζοντες που επιδιώκουν ενοίκιο. Πιστεύουμε στην μείωση των τελών συναλλαγών, την προώθηση του ελεύθερου και διαφανούς εμπορίου, και στο να δωθεί η δυνατότητα στους πρώιμους συμμετέχοντες στην κοινότητα να αποκτήσουν μερίδιο στο δίκτυο.
el-GR.listing-create.chooseSchema: Επιλέξτε μια διάταξη για το προϊόν ή την υπηρεσία σας
el-GR.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Το προϊόν ή την υπηρεσία σας θα χρησιμοποιήσει ένα σχήμα για να περιγράψει χαρακτηριστικά όπως το όνομα, την περιγραφή, και την τιμή. H Origin έχει ήδη πολλά σχήματα που αντιστοιχούν σε γνωστές κατηγορίες καταχωρήσεων όπως στέγαση, οχήματα και υπηρεσίες.
el-GR.listing-create.whatTypeOfListing: Τι είδους καταχώρηση θέλετε να δημιουργήσετε;
el-GR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Η Origin χρησιμοποιεί ένα έργο του Mozilla που ονομάζεται {jsonSchemaLink} να επικυρώστε την καταχώρισή σας σύμφωνα με τους συνήθεις κανόνες. Αυτή η τυποποίηση είναι κλειδί για να επιτρέπονται μη προσυμφωνημένες οντότητες να διαβάσουν και να γράφουν με το ίδιο επίπεδο δεδομένων.
el-GR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Βεβαιωθείτε ότι δώσατε στην καταχώρησή σας κατάλληλο τίτλο και περιγραφή, ώστε να ενημερώνονται οι άλλοι για το τί προσφέρετε.
el-GR.listing-create.successDisclaimer: Η καταχώρισή σας θα είναι ορατή μέσα σε λίγα δευτερόλεπτα.
el-GR.listing-create.error1: Υπήρχε ένα πρόβλημα κατά τη δημιουργία αυτής της καταχώρησης.
el-GR.listing-create.error2: Δείτε την κονσόλα για περισσότερες λεπτομέρειες.
el-GR.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: Όταν πατήσετε submit, ένα αντικείμενο JSON που εκπροσωπεί την καταχώρησή σας θα δημοσιευθεί στο {ipfsLink}  και το κλειδί κατακερματισμού του περιεχομένου θα δημοσιευθεί σε ένα έξυπνο συμβόλαιο λιστών που εκτελείται στο δίκτυο Ethereum.
el-GR.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Παρακαλούμε ελέγξετε την καταχώρησή σας πριν από την υποβολή της. Η καταχώρησή σας θα εμφανίζεται στους άλλους, όπως ακριβώς φαίνεται στο παράθυρο αριστερά.
el-GR.listing-detail.loadingError: Υπήρχε ένα πρόβλημα κατά τη φόρτωση αυτής της καταχώρησης.

el-GR.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

eo-UY.footer.mission: Origin is building the sharing economy of tomorrow. Buyers and sellers will be able to transact without rent-seeking middlemen. We believe in lowering transaction fees, promoting free and transparent commerce, and giving early participants in the community a stake in the network.
eo-UY.listing-create.chooseSchema: Choose a schema for your product or service
eo-UY.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Your product or service will use a schema to describe its attributes like name, description, and price. Origin already has multiple schemas that map to well-known categories of listings like housing, auto, and services.
eo-UY.listing-create.whatTypeOfListing: What type of listing do you want to create?
eo-UY.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin uses a Mozilla project called {jsonSchemaLink}  to validate your listing according to standard rules. This standardization is key to allowing unaffiliated entities to read and write to the same data layer.
eo-UY.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Be sure to give your listing an appropriate title and description that will inform others as to what you’re offering.

eo-UY.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: When you hit submit, a JSON object representing your listing will be published to {ipfsLink}  and the content hash will be published to a listing smart contract running on the Ethereum network.
eo-UY.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Please review your listing before submitting. Your listing will appear to others just as it looks on the window to the left.

eo-UY.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
eo-UY.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

es-ES.footer.mission: En Origin construimos la economía de intercambio del futuro. Tanto compradores como vendedores podrán realizar transacciones sin intermediarios en busca de comisiones. Creemos que se deben reducir las tarifas de transacción, promover un comercio libre y transparente, y en brindar a los primeros participantes de la comunidad la posibilidad de contar con participación en la red.

fil-PH.footer.mission: Ang Origin ay nagtatayo ng sharing economy ng pangkinabukasan. Ang mga nagbebenta at bumibili ay maaring makipagtransaksyon ng walang taong pumapa-gitna. Naniniwala kami sa pagpapababa ng bayad sa transaksyon, pagsulong ng malaya at transparent na komersyo, at pagbibigay ng stake sa network sa mga maagang kalahok sa komunidad.
fil-PH.listing-create.chooseSchema: Pumili ng isang iskema para sa iyong produkto o serbisyo
fil-PH.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Ang iyong produkto o serbisyo ay gagamit ng isang modelo para isalarawan ang mga katangian nito tulad ng pangalan, deskripsyon, at presyo. Ang Origin ay mayroon nang maraming modelo na nakamapa sa mga kilalang kategorya ng mga listahan tulad ng pabahay, sasakyan, at mga serbisyo.
fil-PH.listing-create.whatTypeOfListing: Anong uri ng listahan ang gusto mong gawin?
fil-PH.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Ang Origin ay gumagamit ng proyekto na tinatawag na {jsonSchemaLink} para ma-validate ang inyong listahan ayon sa mga istandard na tuntunin. Ang istandardisasyong ito ay susi para mapahintulutang ang mga unaffiliated entidad na magbasa at magsulat sa parehong layer ng data.
fil-PH.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Tiyaking bigyan ang listahan ng angkop na pamagat at paglalarawan para ipaalam sa iba kung ano ang iyong inaalok.

fil-PH.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: Kapag pinindot mo ang submit, isang JSON object na kumakatawan sa iyong listahan ang mailalathala sa {ipfsLink}  at ang content hash ay ilalathala sa isang listahan sa smart kontrata na tumatakbo sa Ethereum network.
fil-PH.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Mangyaring repasuhin ang iyong listahan bago isumite. Ang iyong listahan ay makikita ng iba tulad ng makikita sa kaliwang window.

fil-PH.messaging-provider.congrats: Maligayang Bati! Maaaring ka ng magmensahe sa iba pang mga gumagamit sa buong plataporma ng Origin ecosystem! Bakit hindi ka magsimula sa pamamagitan ng pagtingin sa paligid at pagsasabi ng sariling opinyong tungkol sa ating DApp?
fil-PH.messaging-provider.welcome:
Maligayang Pagdating sa Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Pinapayagan ka ng aming makabagong messaging platform na makipag-ugnayan sa iba pang mga gumagamit ng Origin sa isang ligtas at desentralisadong paraan. Ang lahat ng iyong mga mensahe ay naka-encrypt at naka-imbak sa IPFS. Ang mga mensahe ay maaari lamang mabasa mo, ang tatanggap, at potensyal na isang arbitrador ng third-party kung alinman sa iyo ay nagsimula ng isang pagtatalo at nagbibigay ng access sa isang cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

Upang paganahin ang pagmemensahe kailangan mong gamitin ang iyong Ethereum wallet upang mag-sign ng dalawang statements. Hindi ito babayaran ng anumang ETH, Origin Token, o gas.

fr-FR.transactions.pendingBlockchainTransactio: En attente des transactions du blockchain
fr-FR.footer.mission: Origin construit l'économie de partage de demain. Acheteurs et vendeurs pourront effectuer des transactions sans intermédiaires. Nous croyons en la diminution des frais de transaction, la promotion un commerce libre et transparent et en donnant aux premiers participants de la communauté une part dans le réseau.

fr-FR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin utilise un projet de Mozilla appelé {jsonSchemaLink}  pour valider votre annonce selon des règles standards. Cette normalisation est la clé permettant aux entités non affiliées de lire et d'écrire dans la même couche de données.

fr-FR.messaging-provider.congrats: Toutes nos félicitations ! Vous pouvez maintenant envoyer un message aux autres utilisateurs de l'écosystème Origin Platform ! Pourquoi ne pas commencer par nous dire ce que vous pensez de notre DApp ?
fr-FR.messaging-provider.welcome:
Bienvenue dans la démo du protocole d'origine DApp ! Notre plate-forme de messagerie innovante vous permet de communiquer avec d'autres utilisateurs Origin de manière sécurisée et décentralisée. Tous vos messages seront cryptés et stockés sur IPFS. Les messages ne peuvent être lus que par vous, le destinataire et éventuellement par un arbitre tiers si l'un d'entre vous initie une dispute et accorde l'accès à une clé privée partagée, générée par cryptographie.

Pour activer la messagerie, vous devez utiliser votre portefeuille Ethereum pour signer deux déclarations. Cela ne coûtera aucun ETH, jeton d'origine ou gaz.

hi-IN.footer.mission: Origin is building the sharing economy of tomorrow. Buyers and sellers will be able to transact without rent-seeking middlemen. We believe in lowering transaction fees, promoting free and transparent commerce, and giving early participants in the community a stake in the network.

hi-IN.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
hi-IN.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

hr-HR.footer.mission: Porijeklo je izgradnja ekonomskog dijeljenja sutra. Kupci i prodavatelji moći će obavljati poslove bez posrednika za iznajmljivanje. Vjerujemo u snižavanje naknada za transakcije, promicanju slobodne i transparentne trgovine i davanje ranih sudionika u zajednici uloga u mreži.
hr-HR.listing-create.chooseSchema: Odaberite shemu za svoj proizvod ili uslugu
hr-HR.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Vaš proizvod ili usluga koristit će shemu za opisivanje atributa kao što su ime, opis i cijena. Podrijetlo već ima više shema koje mapiraju poznate kategorije popisa poput stanovanja, automobila i usluga.
hr-HR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Podrijetlo koristi Mozilla projekt pod nazivom {jsonSchemaLink}  kako bi provjerio vaš unos prema standardnim pravilima. Ova standardizacija ključna je za dopuštanje nepovezanih entiteta da čitaju i pišu na isti podatkovni sloj.
hr-HR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Obavezno unesite svoj unos odgovarajući naslov i opis koji će obavijestiti druge o tome što nudite.

hr-HR.listing-create.error1: Pojavio se problem prilikom izrade ovog unosa.
hr-HR.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: Kada pritisnete slanje, objekt JSON koji predstavlja vaš unos bit će objavljen na {ipfsLink}  a hash sadržaja objavit će se u pametnom ugovoru s popisom koji se izvodi na Ethereum mreži.
hr-HR.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Pregledajte svoj unos prije slanja. Vaš će se popis prikazati drugima baš kao što izgleda u prozoru lijevo.

id-ID.footer.mission: Asal adalah membangun ekonomi berbagi besok. Pembeli dan penjual akan dapat bertransaksi tanpa perantara pencari sewa. Kami percaya dalam menurunkan biaya transaksi, mempromosikan perdagangan yang bebas dan transparan, dan memberi para peserta awal komunitas dalam sebuah saham di jaringan.

it-IT.footer.mission: Origin sta costruendo la sharing economy di domani. Acquirenti e venditori saranno in grado di trattare senza costosi intermediari. Noi crediamo nell'abbassare le spese delle transazioni, nel promuovere un commercio libero e trasparente e nel dare ai primi partecipanti della comunità un ruolo nella rete.

it-IT.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
it-IT.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

ja-JP.messaging-provider.congrats: おめでとうございます！ Originプラットフォームのエコシステム全体で他のユーザにメッセージを送信できるようになりました。 ぜひ私達のDAppについて感想を聞かせてくださいね。
ja-JP.messaging-provider.welcome:
Origin Protocol のデモDAppへようこそ！この革新的なメッセージングプラットフォームを使って、安全かつ分散化された方法で他のOriginユーザとコミュニケーションできます。すべてのメッセージは暗号化され、IPFSに保存されます。もし、ユーザー同士の紛争が発生した場合は、暗号によって生成された共有秘密鍵へのアクセスを許可した場合にのみ、暗号化されたメッセージが、あなた、受取人、および必要な場合は第三者の仲裁人にだけ、読むことができるようになります。
このメッセージ機能を有効にするには、Ethereumウォレットを使用して2つのステートメントに署名する必要があります。
この署名にはEthereum、Originトークン、またはガスなどの費用はかかりません。

ko-KR.footer.mission: Origin 은 미래의 공유 경제를 구축중입니다. 구매자와 판매자들은 지대추구형(*경제용어: 불공정거래의 한 형태) 중개자들 없이 거래하게 될 것입니다. 거래 수수료를 낮추고, 자유롭고 투명한 상거래를 촉진하며, 커뮤니티에 초기 참여한 사람들에게 네트워크 지분을 분배하게 될 것이라고 믿습니다.
ko-KR.listing-create.schemaExplainer: 당신의 제품이나 서비스는 이름, 설명 및 가격과 같은 특성을 설명하는 스키마를 사용합니다. Origin은 주택, 자동차 및 서비스와 같이 친숙한 카테고리로 구성된 다수의 스키마들을 이미 보유하고 있습니다.
ko-KR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin은 {jsonSchemaLink} 라는 Mozilla 프로젝트를 사용하여 표준 규칙에 따라 귀하의 목록을 확인합니다. 이 표준화는 소속되지 않은 개체가 동일한 데이터 레이어를 읽고 쓸 수 있게 하는 핵심 요소입니다.
ko-KR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: 당신이 무엇을 제공하는지를 다른 사람들이 알 수 있도록 적합한 제목과 설명으로 목록을 작성하십시오.
ko-KR.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: Submit을 누르면, 목록을 나타내는 JSON 개체가 {ipfsLink} 로 게시되고 콘텐트 해시는 Ethereum 네트워크에서 실행되는 리스팅 스마트 계약에 게시됩니다.
ko-KR.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: 제출하기 전에 목록을 확인하십시오. 당신의 목록은 왼쪽 창에 보이는 것처럼 다른 사람에게 보여집니다.

ko-KR.listings-grid.changeNetworks: 네트워크 변경 혹은 계약 실행이 필요할 수 있습니다.

ko-KR.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
ko-KR.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

lo-LA.footer.mission: Origin is building the sharing economy of tomorrow. Buyers and sellers will be able to transact without rent-seeking middlemen. We believe in lowering transaction fees, promoting free and transparent commerce, and giving early participants in the community a stake in the network.
lo-LA.listing-create.chooseSchema: Choose a schema for your product or service
lo-LA.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Your product or service will use a schema to describe its attributes like name, description, and price. Origin already has multiple schemas that map to well-known categories of listings like housing, auto, and services.
lo-LA.listing-create.whatTypeOfListing: What type of listing do you want to create?
lo-LA.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin uses a Mozilla project called {jsonSchemaLink}  to validate your listing according to standard rules. This standardization is key to allowing unaffiliated entities to read and write to the same data layer.
lo-LA.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Be sure to give your listing an appropriate title and description that will inform others as to what you’re offering.

lo-LA.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

nl-NL.footer.mission: Origin bouwt aan de deeleconomie van morgen. Kopers en verkopers zullen in staat gesteld worden transacties uit te voeren zonder een tussenpersoon die uit is op winst. Wij geloven in het omlaag brengen van transactiekosten, stimuleren vrije en transparante handel en geven vroegtijdige deelnemers een aandeel in het netwerk.
nl-NL.listing-create.chooseSchema: Maak een keuze voor uw product of service
nl-NL.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Uw product of dienst maakt gebruik van een systeem om gegevens zoals de naam, omschrijving en prijs te kenmerken. Origin beschikt al over een systeem wat navigeert naar bekende productcategorieën zoals vastgoed, auto's en diensten.

nl-NL.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin gebruikt een Mozilla-project genaamd {jsonSchemaLink} om uw advertentie volgens standaardregels te valideren. Deze standaardisatie is nodig om niet-aangesloten deelnemers te laten lezen en schrijven op dezelfde datalaag.
nl-NL.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Zorg ervoor dat u uw advertentie een adequate titel en beschrijving geeft zodat voor anderen duidelijk is wat u aanbiedt.

nl-NL.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Controleer uw advertentie voor het indienen. Uw advertentie zal voor anderen zichtbaar zijn zoals in het linker venster weergegeven.

pl-PL.footer.mission: Origin is building the sharing economy of tomorrow. Buyers and sellers will be able to transact without rent-seeking middlemen. We believe in lowering transaction fees, promoting free and transparent commerce, and giving early participants in the community a stake in the network.

pl-PL.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
pl-PL.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

ro-RO.footer.mission: Origin construiește economia colaborativă a viitorului. Cumpărătorii și vânzătorii vor avea posibilitatea să tranzacționeze fără intermediari care nu ajută la dezvoltarea economiei. Credem în scăderea taxelor de tranzacționare promovând comerțul liber și transparent și oferim primilor membri ai comunității o poziționare preferențială în rețea.
ro-RO.listing-create.chooseSchema: Alegeți un șablon pentru produsul sau serviciul dumneavoastră
ro-RO.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Produsul sau serviciul dumneavoastră va folosi un șablon pentru a descrie atributele sale cum ar fi numele, descrierea și prețul. Origin pune la dispoziție o serie de șabloane care se mulează pe diverse categorii bine cunoscute de anunțuri cum ar fi locuințe, auto și servicii.
ro-RO.listing-create.whatTypeOfListing: Ce tip de anunț doriţi să creaţi?
ro-RO.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin utilizează un proiect de Mozilla denumit {jsonSchemaLink}  pentru a valida anunțul dumneavoastră în conformitate cu regulile standard. Această standardizare este cheia pentru a permite entităţi neafiliate să citească şi să scrie la același nivel de date.
ro-RO.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Asigurați-va că alegeți un titlu potrivit pentru anunțul dumneavoastră și o descriere care să le sugereze celorlalți ce oferiți.

ro-RO.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Vă rugăm să vă revizuiți anunțul înainte de a-l trimite. Anunțul dumneavoastră va fi afișat celorlalți utilizatori așa cum arată în fereastra din stânga.

ru-RU.footer.mission: Origin строит будущую экономику совместного потребления. Покупатели и продавцы смогут взаимодействовать без посредников, взымающих плату за свою работу. Мы верим в уменьшение комиссий за транзакции, занимаемся продвижением свободной и честной коммерческой деятельности, и даем ранним участникам сообщества долю в сети.
ru-RU.listing-create.chooseSchema: Выберите схему для Вашего продукта или услуги
ru-RU.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Ваш продукт или услуга будут использовать схему для описания таких атрибутов, как имя, описание и цена. В Origin уже есть множество схем, охватывающих хорошо известные категории, такие как аренда жилья, автомобилей, оказание услуг.

ru-RU.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: В Origin используется проект Mozilla под названием {jsonSchemaLink} для проверки Вашего объявления на соответствие стандартным правилам. Эта стандартизация - ключ к тому, чтобы независимые объекты имели возможность производить чтение и запись на одном и том же уровне данных.
ru-RU.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Удостоверьтесь в том, что Ваше объявление названо и описано должным образом, чтобы дать информацию другим о том, что Вы предлагаете.

ru-RU.listing-create.error2: См. консоль для получения более детальной информации.
ru-RU.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: Когда Вы нажмете Отправить, объект JSON, представляющий ваше объявление, будет опубликован на {ipfsLink} и содержание хэша будет опубликовано в смарт-контракте объявления, работающем на сети Ethereum.
ru-RU.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Пожалуйста, проверьте ваше объявление перед отправкой. Ваше объявление будет отображаться для других людей так же, как оно выглядит в окне слева.

ru-RU.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
ru-RU.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

sk-SK.footer.mission: Origin is building the sharing economy of tomorrow. Buyers and sellers will be able to transact without rent-seeking middlemen. We believe in lowering transaction fees, promoting free and transparent commerce, and giving early participants in the community a stake in the network.
sk-SK.listing-create.chooseSchema: Choose a schema for your product or service
sk-SK.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Your product or service will use a schema to describe its attributes like name, description, and price. Origin already has multiple schemas that map to well-known categories of listings like housing, auto, and services.

sk-SK.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin uses a Mozilla project called {jsonSchemaLink}  to validate your listing according to standard rules. This standardization is key to allowing unaffiliated entities to read and write to the same data layer.

Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

sl-SI.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
sl-SI.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

th-TH.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
th-TH.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

tr-TR.footer.mission: Köken, yarının paylaşım ekonomisini inşa ediyor. Alıcılar ve satıcılar aracı arayışına girmeden işlem yapabilirler. İşlem ücretlerinin düşürülmesine, serbest ve şeffaf ticaretin teşvik edilmesine ve topluluğa erken katılımcılar için ağda bir pay verilmesine inanıyoruz.
tr-TR.listing-create.chooseSchema: Ürün veya hizmetiniz için bir şema seçin
tr-TR.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Ürününüz veya hizmetiniz, adı, açıklaması ve fiyatı gibi özelliklerini açıklayan bir şema kullanacaktır. Kökeni zaten konut, otomatik ve hizmetler gibi iyi bilinen kategoriler listeleyen birçok şemaya sahiptir.
tr-TR.listing-create.whatTypeOfListing: Ne tür bir liste oluşturmak istiyorsunuz?
tr-TR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin, girişinizi standart kurallara göre doğrulamak için {jsonSchemaLink}  adlı bir Mozilla projesi kullanıyor. Bu standardizasyon, bağımsız kuruluşların aynı veri katmanını okumasına ve yazmasına izin vermenin anahtarıdır.
tr-TR.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Girişinizi, sunduğunuz ürün ve hizmetleri diğerlerine bildirecek uygun bir başlık ve açıklama verdiğinizden emin olun.
tr-TR.listing-create.error1: Bu girişi oluştururken bir sorun oluştu.
tr-TR.listing-create.error2: Daha fazla bilgi için konsola bakın.
tr-TR.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: Gönderdiğinizde, girişinizi temsil eden bir JSON nesnesi {ipfsLink}  olarak yayınlanacak ve içerik karması, Ethereum ağında çalışan bir giriş akıllı sözleşmesine yayınlanacaktır.
tr-TR.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Lütfen göndermeden önce girişinizi gözden geçirin. Girişiniz, soldaki pencerede göründüğü gibi başkalarına görünecektir.

tr-TR.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
tr-TR.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

ug-CN.footer.mission: Origin is building the sharing economy of tomorrow. Buyers and sellers will be able to transact without rent-seeking middlemen. We believe in lowering transaction fees, promoting free and transparent commerce, and giving early participants in the community a stake in the network.

Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

uk-UA.footer.mission: Origin будує економіку обміну майбутнього. Покупці та продавці матимуть можливість виконувати транзакції без допомоги посередників, чиї послуги треба оплачувати. Ми віримо в зменшенна комісій за транзакції, сприяємо вільній та прозорій комерційній діяльності, та надаємо раннім учасникам спільноти частку в мережі.
uk-UA.listing-create.chooseSchema: Оберіть схему для Вашого продукту чи послуги

vi-VN.footer.mission: Origin là xây dựng nền kinh tế chia sẻ của tương lai. Người mua và người bán sẽ có thể giao dịch mà không cần có người trung gian cho việc tìm kiếm. Chúng tôi tin rằng trong việc giảm phí giao dịch, thúc đẩy thương mại tự do, minh bạch, và cho những người tham gia ban đầu trong cộng đồng một cổ phần trong network.
vi-VN.listing-create.chooseSchema: Chọn một lược đồ cho sản phẩm hoặc dịch vụ của bạn
vi-VN.listing-create.schemaExplainer: Sản phẩm hoặc dịch vụ của bạn sẽ sử dụng một sơ đồ để miêu tả các đặc tính của nó như tên, mô tả và giá cả. Origin đã có sẵn nhiều lược đồ dẫn tới tới các danh mục của các danh sách phổ biến như nhà ở, ô tô và dịch vụ.

vi-VN.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin sử dụng dự án {jsonSchemaLink} của Mozilla để xác thực danh sách của bạn theo chuẩn quy tắc. Việc chuẩn hóa này là chìa khóa để cho phép các tổ chức không được liên kết đọc và ghi vào cùng một lớp dữ liệu.
vi-VN.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: Hãy chắc chắn cung cấp cho danh sách của bạn một tiêu đề và mô tả phù hợp để thông báo cho những người khác về những gì bạn đang cung cấp.

vi-VN.listing-create.error2: Xem bảng điều khiển để biết thêm thông tin chi tiết.

vi-VN.listing-create.whatHappensNextHeading: Điều gì xảy ra tiếp theo?
vi-VN.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: Khi bạn nhấn gửi đi, một file JSON đại diện cho danh sách của bạn sẽ được xuất bản lên {ipfsLink} và việc băm nội dung sẽ được xuất bản tới một danh sách hợp đồng thông minh chạy trên mạng lưới Ethereum.
vi-VN.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: Vui lòng xem lại danh sách của bạn trước khi gửi. Danh sách của bạn sẽ xuất hiện cho người xem giống cửa sổ bên trái.

vi-VN.messaging-provider.congrats: Xin chúc mừng! Bây giờ bạn có thể nhắn tin cho những người dùng khác trên toàn hệ thống của Origin! Hãy khám phá và để lại suy nghĩ của mình về ứng dụng của chúng tôi?
vi-VN.messaging-provider.welcome:
Chào mừng đến với ứng dụng Demo của Origin! Nền tảng nhắn tin của chúng tôi cho phép bạn kết nối với những người dùng khác trên Origin một cách an toàn và phi tập trung. Tất cả những tin nhắn của bạn sẽ được mã hóa và lưu trên IPFS. Tin nhắn chỉ được xem bởi bạn, người nhận hoặc bên thứ ba trong trường hợp có tranh chấp và chỉ cấp quyền truy cập cho một mật mã duy nhất được tạo ra.

Để bật tính năng nhắn tin bạn cần sử dụng ví của Ethereum để kí hai xác nhận. Điều này sẽ không tốn phí.

zh-CN.footer.mission: 起源正在建造未来的共享经济。买方和卖方将能够在没有中间商的情况下进行交易。我们相信，降低交易费用，促进自由和透明的商业活动，并给予社区的早期参与者在网络中的股份。

zh-CN.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
zh-CN.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.

zh-TW.footer.mission: Origin正在構建明天的共享經濟。 買家和賣家可以在沒有尋租中介人的情況下進行交易。 我們相信降低交易費用，促進自由和透明的商業，並讓社區的早期參與者參與網絡。
zh-TW.listing-create.chooseSchema: 選擇你的產品或服務模式
zh-TW.listing-create.schemaExplainer: 您的產品或服務將使用模式來描述其屬性，如名稱，說明和價格。 Origin已經有多種模式，可以映射到眾所周知的房源類別，如房屋，汽車和服務。
zh-TW.listing-create.whatTypeOfListing: 你想新增什麼類型的發佈?
zh-TW.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart1: Origin使用Mozilla的一個項目稱為 {jsonSchemaLink} 根據標準規則驗證您的列登。 這種標準化是允許非附屬實體讀取和寫入相同數據層的關鍵。
zh-TW.listing-create.howItWorksContentPart2: 確保你的刊登一個適當的標題和簡介，以告知他人你提供的是什麼。
zh-TW.listing-create.successDisclaimer: 您的商家信息將在幾秒鐘內顯示。
zh-TW.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent1: 當您點擊提交時，代表你的列表的JSON對象將被發佈到 {ipfsLink} ，並且內容哈希將被發佈到在以太坊網絡上運行的列表智能合約。
zh-TW.listing-create.whatHappensNextContent2: 提交前請檢查您的刊登。 您的刊登將顯示給其他人，就像它在左側窗口中顯示的一樣。
zh-TW.listing-detail.successDisclaimer: 您的購買將在幾秒鐘內顯示。

zh-TW.messaging-provider.congrats: Congratulations! You can now message other users across the Origin Platform ecosystem! Why not start by taking a look around and telling us what you think about our DApp?
zh-TW.messaging-provider.welcome:
Welcome to the Origin Protocol Demo DApp! Our innovative messaging platform allows you to communicate with other Origin users in a secure and decentralized way. All of your messages will be encrypted and stored on IPFS. Messages can only be read by you, the recipient, and potentially a third-party arbitrator if either of you initiates a dispute and grants access to a cryptographically-generated, shared, private key.

In order to enable messaging you will need to use your Ethereum wallet to sign two statements. This will not cost any ETH, Origin Token, or gas.
